metadata.name: Clementrinessence
metadata.description:
How does it feel when longing leaves no escape routes?
How does a creature who has forgotten about the world, left alone, transform?
Is he an angel or just a monster who encroached on a forbidden feeling?
Will his fragile rose allow him to dissolve in her blossom and petals?
Or will she reveal them, penetrate him and dissolve herself in him, becoming his secret essence?
